rComments: Very enthusiastic, but doesn't know how to teach. As said before by others, she is quite unprofessional, randomly laughs and pauses. Powerpoint sides and flow of lecture is unclear. Myself, having a musical background in royal conservatory voice and piano I thought I would enjoy this class, not the case.

The lectures are really dragged on, boring, and a lot of times she doesn't make sense. A lot of weird anecdotes which most of the time make the concept way more complicated/confusing than it is. Also, she awkwardly pauses for long periods of time and laughs, it's pretty unprofessional. Very nice person though, accessible as well.
Extermely unprofessional. Lectures are extremely boring and she just doesn't know how to teach. Always laughing while she's lecturing too so it is unclear. She is nice though.
